				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Start\", enter the tombstone shop and go down into the Murder Tribunal\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Dolor 1\" to get Dolor to appear at the Death Knight guarding the courtroom.\r\n- Walk up near them without getting spotted, and this AD will play."
