					"type": 23,
					"value": "If the party has killed two of the murder targets themselves, Dolor will come to the Murder Tribunal instead of his usual questline. When we approach, we can overhear Dolor and the Death Knight discussing that there is another aspirant seeking the Murder Tribunal."
